{"tid":1247790,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"比人屌三毛 我都要講嫁喇","createTime":"2019-06-21T08:35:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T09:04:52.000Z","uid":161502,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"887db1c0a15a10e54da303780286a6bbf7e93a4e","tid":1247790,"uid":161502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T08:35:30.000Z","msg":"點解要佔稅務大樓？ 我想講政府未驚過<br />\n稅收概況： 2017-18年度本局的整體稅收為3,286億元<br />\n財政儲備： 至2020年3月底升至11,784億元<br />\n即係話 除非你地佔足3年，唔係既話，政府都仲大把老本食<br />\n大家今日辛辛苦苦幫稅局d人提早兩個鐘收工，過兩日佢地咪OT追返進度<br />\n仲到搞到返工既人上唔到去拎袋拎藥，嘈來嘈去<br />\n萬一打起上黎，咁辛苦積落既民意都無晒<br />\n要示威就係人地開工前，要去就去少市民多官員既地方<br />\n<br />\n今日睇到大家同d員工嘈，夾硬唔比人上返去，個感覺真係好差<br />\n直言相諫，大家即管話我三毛<br />\n<br />\nSource係度<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ird.gov.hk/chi/abo/rev.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ird.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fabo%2Frev.htm&d=ciqixHjE7SQ%2Bh8bl84MOeyEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=1a427b71\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ird.gov.hk/chi/abo/rev.htm</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/299959/%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88-%E4%BE%86%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%99%E9%8C%84168%E5%84%84%E5%85%83%E7%9B%88%E9%A4%98-%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E5%84%B2%E5%82%99%E5%8D%87%E8%87%B311784%E5%84%84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F299959%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E4%25BE%2586%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2596%2599%25E9%258C%2584168%25E5%2584%2584%25E5%2585%2583%25E7%259B%2588%25E9%25A4%2598-%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%2584%25B2%25E5%2582%2599%25E5%258D%2587%25E8%2587%25B311784%25E5%2584%2584&d=ciqixHjE7SQ%2Bh8bl84MOeyEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=1e84c783\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/299959/%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88-%E4%BE%86%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%99%E9%8C%84168%E5%84%84%E5%85%83%E7%9B%88%E9%A4%98-%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E5